Package: polyvar
Type: Package
Title: Contrastive Variance QTL Detection (vQTL) via PolyVAR
Version: 0.5.0
Date: 2026-03-24
Authors@R: c(
    person("PolyVAR", "Development Team", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "polyvar@deylab.org"))
Description: Implements PolyVAR and PolyVAR-lite, contrastive variance QTL
    (vQTL) tests that eliminate contamination from co-located mean QTL effects
    via score-space projection. Also provides Levene+RINT, Brown-Forsythe+RINT,
    Bartlett+RINT, and DGLM for benchmarking. Reads PLINK BED/BIM/FAM and BGEN
    genotype files in streaming batches. Provides both R functions and a
    command-line interface (polyvar).
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/Deylab999/PolyVAR
BugReports: https://github.com/Deylab999/PolyVAR/issues
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.0), RcppArmadillo, data.table (>= 1.14.0),
        optparse (>= 1.7.0), Matrix
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), knitr, rmarkdown
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
SystemRequirements: C++14
NeedsCompilation: yes
